UPDATING THE APP
-------------------------
make changes 

Update the image 
    $ docker build -t getting-started . 
        # same as before 

Remove the old Container 
    get the id 
        $ docker ps
    stop and remove it (could be done with 2 commands, `stop` and `rm`)
        $ docker rm -f <the-container-id>
    check it's not there
        $ docker ps 

Run it (no '.')
    $ docker run -dp 3000:3000 getting-started